I tripped up every time trying to say vole vasopressin, probably because I didnt have enough coffee yet. 1b stats are displayed just using summary() and std error of mean was calculated with sd(val)/length(val). The standard error of the mean tells us that our mean value estimate is not very representative of our data because the sampling distribution of our mean is too large.
